{
  "stem": "17001.7",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 214.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Just put the blanket on your shoulder and go that way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was one occasion when I realized that by going to the bunker, that's the best time to steal potatoes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because we had the potato [HUNGARIAN] next to our barrack.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I would ran to the [HUNGARIAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would put the few potatoes into my coat pocket.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I would run with the other girls to the-- to the shelter.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At one occasion, I had taken a few potatoes from the-- from the [HUNGARIAN].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was running.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But by that time, all the girls went into the-- to the shelter.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I was banging on the door, and two of these [GERMAN] opened the door.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they gave me a beating, and they kicked me under my knee, that I fell on my nose.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They said that I fall asleep, and I'm a lousy lazy this and this and this and this.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I-- finally I crawled out and I went to the other entrance of the-- of the shelter.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Over there, the [GERMAN] opened the door and gave me a hit, and I went in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this happened quite often.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But what happened this particular time, the [GERMAN] that had kicked me and gave me a beating and called me all kinds of lazy thing, when the bomb was coming we felt it that it's going to hit us.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because when you have so many [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] days and nights of experience with the bombing, your ear gets so used to it you know already how far the bomb is dropping.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that particular time, we felt that the way the wind, the pressure, was coming, that we are being hit.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we didn't know where or how.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We came out of the shelter.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
